summary: Adds over 100 bunnies to the major holds of Skyrim!
descriptionHtml:
[font=Courier New][center]The people of Skyrim have decided that they need to protect the bunnies from the dragons by bringing them inside their walls. (or something.. I don't know)

[size=3]Adds bunnies to the following locations:[/size]
Whiterun
Solitude
Markarth
Riften
Windhelm
[b][u]
Basically, all the big cities have been overrun with bunnies.[/u][/b]
-All bunnies respawn
-different sizes and colors
-can't open doors
[color=#ff0000][b][u]
[/u][/b][/color][size=3][color=#ff0000][b][u]Install:[/u][/b][/color]
[/size]1. make sure you are not outside in any of these cities or you will most likely CTD (SAVE INDOORS)
2. Install with NMM or manually extract into Skyrim/Data
3. load game INDOORS
4. enjoy the bunnies
[b][u][color=#00ff00]
[size=3]Requirements:[/size][/color][/u][/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61035/?]JK's Skyrim[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58322/?]Rabbits of Skyrim[/url]
